<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Wallpaper API</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 800px;
      margin: 50px auto;
      padding: 20px;
      background-color: #f9f9f9;
      border-radius: 8px;
      box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }
    h1 {
      color: #333;
    }
    p {
      color: #666;
    }
    ul {
      list-style-type: none;
      padding: 0;
    }
    li {
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    a {
      color: #007bff;
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: color 0.3s ease;
    }
    a:hover {
      color: #0056b3;
    }

    /* Responsive Styles */
    @media screen and (max-width: 600px) {
      .container {
        max-width: 100%;
        margin: 20px;
        border-radius: 0;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h1>About Wallpaper API</h1>
    <p>Welcome to the Wallpaper API, where you can access various wallpapers!</p>

    <h2>Navigation</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><a href="/api/">GET</a> - Get all API data from the server</li>
      <li><a href="/api/upload/">POST</a> - Upload new data to the server</li>
      <li><a href="/api/testing/">Testing</a> - Testing purposes</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
